en especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes Lamborne was born in 1296 as the daughter of Ralph Lamborne and wife Ralph Lamborne. She married Sir Henry de Raleigh before 1315, in Europe. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1296–":"1296–Surnud","1296–Female":"1296–Surnud","1289–1376":"1289–1376","1315–Male":"1315–Surnud","1275–Male":"1275–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","before 1315":"enne 1315","1315":"1315","1289":"1289","1376":"1376","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","before 1296":"enne 1296","Europe":"Europe","England":"England"},"fi":{"1296–":"1296–Kuollut","1296–Female":"1296–Kuollut","1289–1376":"1289–1376","1315–Male":"1315–Kuollut","1275–Male":"1275–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","before 1315":"ennen vuotta 1315","1315":"1315","1289":"1289","1376":"1376","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","before 1296":"ennen vuotta 1296","Europe":"Europe","England":"England"},"fr":{"1296–":"1296–Décédée","1296–Female":"1296–Décédée","1289–1376":"1289–1376","1315–Male":"1315–Décédé","1275–Male":"1275–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","before 1315":"avant 1315","1315":"1315","1289":"1289","1376":"1376","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","before 1296":"avant 1296","Europe":"Europe","England":"Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Agnes Lamborne est née en 1296, fille de Ralph Lamborne et wife Ralph Lamborne. Elle a épousé Sir Henry de Raleigh avant 1315, à Europe. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1296–":"1296–Verstorben","1296–Female":"1296–Verstorben","1289–1376":"1289–1376","1315–Male":"1315–Verstorben","1275–Male":"1275–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","before 1315":"vor 1315","1315":"1315","1289":"1289","1376":"1376","1275":"1275","1296":"1296","before 1296":"vor 1296","Europe":"Europa","England":"England","lifeSummary":"Agnes Lamborne wurde 1296, als Tochter von Ralph Lamborne und wife Ralph Lamborne geboren. Sie hat vor 1315 in Europa Sir Henry de Raleigh geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1296–":"1296–Desede","1296–Female":"1296–D